Connection Back to the Narrative Tensor Engine

If we think in NTE terms:

story_state = tensor(character, time, tension, theme, perspective)

A wraith state looks something like:

identity → decreasing
agency → decreasing
external control → increasing
goal fixation → increasing

That trajectory collapses into a single attractor: servitude.

The character loses dimensionality.

⸻

The Structural Mirror

The council scene you shared is interesting because it sits at a pivot point:
	•	Kings debating fate of the Ring
	•	The same kind of kings who once became wraiths

So the story moment sits between two possible attractors:

leadership → sacrifice → restoration

or

power → corruption → wraith

That tension is exactly what drives the narrative.

